         Elder Wolf Hide (4INT, 30HP + more) for 2K.<BR>Cape of the Corpsemaster (8AC, 30HP, 30Mana, 2STR) for 2K.<BR>Obulus Death Shroud (5STA, 25Mana, Mana Preservation III, +more) for 8K ish.</P><P>The 8th Shawl is nice, no questions, but these quests take a long ass time. Before you even bother doing a single thing with these quests, get tailoring up to 150+ (trivial is at 158). If you have the enthusiam after that, then do the quests. If you cannot be bothered to get your tailoring up, then you have wasted no time doing the quests.</P><P>Cheers,<BR>Ancagalon the Black<BR>Warlock - Terris Thule</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
